bug.short_desc: Some part of dialog is clipped when select stock chart with secondary Axis.

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 85959 correct
description: Some part of dialog is clipped when select stock chart with secondary Axis.
build version: 2.2.2 v20071218-1951
steps to reproduce: 1. New a report. 2. Insert a chart to the report. 3. On Select Type tab, select Stock chart and select secondary axis, click next. 4. Check the Select Data tab.
Expected result: See attached screenshot:correct.
Actual result: See attached screenshot:incorrect.

This is caused by that the space for header Area is not enough in Sash Form when the sash is at the middle position.
Solution: When the space is not enough, set the correct position of sash and the correct size of Sash Form.
verified on build 2.3.0 v20080201-0800 and closed.
